C-16 acetate derivative tumacoside A ( 3 ) displayed in vitro antimalarial activity against
Plasmodium falciparum
chloroquine-resistant FCB-1 strain, with IC 50 = 27 μM. In addition to hydroxylation at C-16, conjugated 3-keto-steroids with a hydroxy group at C-6 have been reported from the red algae
Jania adhaerens
from the Red Sea (
